commentText: Welcome to Boston!!!!   Check out "Explorateur Cafe" it's relatively new, right next to Boston Common.   Also check out the Dim Sum places ("China Pearl") around here, they are generally authentic and come around with carts of delicious food (tip: just say "yes" because you can't understand them--unless you speak their language).  Cambridge MUST GO: Life Alive--you literally need this in your life. Mostly Vegan, 100% Vegetarian, and a lot of gluten free options. ALL GOOD. Get the Spring Alive smoothie.
